t:
Your eyes filled with such delight,
My heart told me you were the one,
And I knew that we'd be alright.

I love the way you make me feel,
Your touch is like a drug to me,
And I'm addicted, I can't tell,
How much longer I can be free.
c:
I love the way you look at me,
Your eyes full of such care,
The way you smile makes me feel,
That I'm the only one there.
